      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is always so busy and it's such a hassle to get an appointment just for a small dose change. i'm pretty good at tracking my own stuff, and since i've been so active and eating the same things, i feel like my levels must be stable. if i were to just try the 2mg for a week to see how i feel, would that be a huge risk or is it pretty standard to taper down like that when things are going well?",
